# Environment Variables Template — OprexDuit

Copy file ini ke `.env.local` (frontend) atau `.env` (backend) dan isi nilainya.
File `.env.local` sudah ada di .gitignore — aman.

---

## Frontend (.env.local)

```env
# Backend API URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# Supabase (wajib — ambil dari Supabase dashboard → Settings → API)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://<project-id>.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...
```

## Backend (.env) — juga set di Render dashboard sebagai env vars

```env
# CORS — set ke URL Vercel production
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://oprexduit.vercel.app,http://localhost:3000

# Supabase (wajib — ambil dari Supabase dashboard → Settings → API)
SUPABASE_URL=https://<project-id>.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key   # JANGAN commit ke git
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret              # Settings → API → JWT Secret

# AI Provider
# Set AI_PROVIDER ke salah satu: glm | deepseek | gemini
AI_PROVIDER=glm

# --- Opsi A: Kelola API key via Admin Console (REKOMENDASI) ---
# Simpan keys di Supabase, rotate via UI tanpa redeploy.
# Cukup set ADMIN_SECRET dan daftarkan keys lewat Admin Console /api-keys.
# ADMIN_SECRET dipakai Admin Console untuk autentikasi endpoint /admin/*
ADMIN_SECRET=your-strong-random-secret   # isi juga di Admin Console → Settings → Bearer Token

# GLM API endpoint (default: api.z.ai proxy)
# Jika punya akses langsung ke open.bigmodel.cn, ganti di sini.
GLM_BASE_URL=https://api.z.ai/api/openai/v1
GLM_MODEL=glm-4.7

# --- Opsi B: Fallback env vars (jika DB kosong / Supabase tidak tersambung) ---
GLM_API_KEY=your-glm-key-1              # set di Render
GLM_API_KEY_2=your-glm-key-2            # opsional — fallback key 2
GLM_API_KEY_3=your-glm-key-3            # opsional — fallback key 3
GLM_API_KEY_4=your-glm-key-4            # opsional — fallback key 4
GLM_API_KEY_5=your-glm-key-5            # opsional — fallback key 5
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-deepseek-key
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key

# Payment (Phase 6)
MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY=your-midtrans-key
MIDTRANS_CLIENT_KEY=your-midtrans-client-key
MIDTRANS_IS_PRODUCTION=false
```

> Lihat SECRETS.md (lokal, tidak di-commit) untuk nilai production lengkap.
